om/blog/2026/03/within-person-association-between-daily-screen-use-and-sleep-in-youth-a-systematic-review-and-meta-analysis</link><description>一项荟萃分析发现，在屏幕使用较多的日子里，青少年上床睡觉的时间会稍晚一些，但总睡眠时间、睡眠质量或效率没有显着变化。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/within-person-association-between-daily-screen-use-and-sleep-in-youth-a-systematic-review-and-meta-analysis.png" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 23:23:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/within-person-association-between-daily-screen-use-and-sleep-in-youth-a-systematic-review-and-meta-analysis</guid></item><item><title>广泛使用的手术并不能抑制胰腺分裂症患者的胰腺炎</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/widely-used-procedure-does-not-curb-pancreatitis-in-patients-with-pancreas-divisum</link><description>一项新的随机、假对照研究得出结论，对于患有胰腺分裂的不明原因急性复发性胰腺炎患者，广泛使用的内镜逆行胰胆管造影（ERCP）联合小乳头切开术并不能降低急性胰腺炎更多发作的风险或防止长期后果。这些发现与主要基于观察数据的长期信念相悖。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/widely-used-procedure-does-not-curb-pancreatitis-in-patients-with-pancreas-divisum.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 23:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/widely-used-procedure-does-not-curb-pancreatitis-in-patients-with-pancreas-divisum</guid></item><item><title>大爆炸之前存在什么？这没什么……还是更令人不安的事情？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/what-existed-before-the-big-bang-was-it-nothing-or-something-far-more-disturbing</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 22:53:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/what-existed-before-the-big-bang-was-it-nothing-or-something-far-more-disturbing</guid></item></channel></rss>